d calmness under pressure, which are non\u2011negotiable for long\u2011distance, high\u2011responsibility flights. However, the teamwork concerns are serious, so I\u2019m interested in any additional reliability information that could shift the balance.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
