ervations or assessments?\n3. **Operational impact** of Candidate\u202fB\u2019s weak numeric memory \u2013 could this affect navigation, fuel calculations, or other critical numeric tasks?\nIf anyone has any of this missing information, it could help us reassess the balance between the strong reliability/composure of Candidate\u202fB and the teamwork/health concerns across all candidates.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
